name: Baby Floki
description: What is the project about? Introducing "Baby Floki" - a revolutionary step forward in the world of cryptocurrency. Just as Floki Inus are known for their loyalty, Baby Floki aims to create a steadfast community united by a shared passion for crypto innovation. What makes your project unique? Tokenomics Baby Floki ($BABYFLOKI) features a total supply of 420,690,000,000,000 tokens, operating on the secure Ethereum (ETH) blockchain. The contract ownership has been renounced, emphasizing transparency, while the liquidity pool (LP) is locked to ensure stability. With a 1% transaction tax, Baby Floki rewards holders and contributes to the project's growth. Join the Baby Floki community today to be a part of this exciting journey in the crypto world.
